lead_paragraph: VICHY, France, Nov. 21 -- General Maxime Weygand having retired and the Pro-Consulate in French Africa having been abolished, there was a political lull today, permitting consideration of implications, reactions and possibilities.
abstract: N Y C Fight For Freedom Com hears Germans will move into Dakar
